name: Lightning Loot Ladies
description:
These three fabulous, feisty, flashy jewelry thieves are at it again! This time they hit the vault of some very powerful Russians & rumor is they made off with over $400 Million in precious gems. Keep your eyes peeled because these lighting fast crooks are just getting started.
